    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/44934c2c244bf0899d3d92008c5ce310.avif?t=1748268012\" width=488 height=82 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Genre:</strong> Roguelike, Aquatic Eat Em Up.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Gameplay</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Progression</strong></u>  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Eating fish rewards you experience &amp; heals you, which varies per fish and level. Each level bigger fish will spawn.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/e941c6c42ceb394da3291ae47360bb5a.poster.avif?t=1748268012\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/e941c6c42ceb394da3291ae47360bb5a.webm?t=1748268012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/e941c6c42ceb394da3291ae47360bb5a.mp4?t=1748268012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Combat</strong></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will face an array of different hostile and neutral fish. Ranging from a shark-eating sperm whale to a short-sighted coral groupers.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/1b545a8c62fad4a2728f4348da59fe7b.poster.avif?t=1748268012\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/1b545a8c62fad4a2728f4348da59fe7b.webm?t=1748268012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/1b545a8c62fad4a2728f4348da59fe7b.mp4?t=1748268012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Boss Fight</strong></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >When you reach level 10, you will be faced with a sperm whale that really hates sharks.   </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/0ef4f784caa3c0bf88e99e1289302392.poster.avif?t=1748268012\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/0ef4f784caa3c0bf88e99e1289302392.webm?t=1748268012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/0ef4f784caa3c0bf88e99e1289302392.mp4?t=1748268012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Difficulty Modes</strong></u><strong> (v1.1.0)</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Story Mode</strong> is for people that don't play games.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Normal Mode</strong> is more forgiving and balanced.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Nightmare Mode</strong> will challenge experienced players.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/74f0fb79cdae90ac5af8cc5e421e60ec.poster.avif?t=1748268012\" width=616 height=252 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/74f0fb79cdae90ac5af8cc5e421e60ec.webm?t=1748268012\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2307830/extras/74f0fb79cdae90ac5af8cc5e421e60ec.mp4?t=1748268012\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Controls (WASD Only)</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>W Key:</strong> Sprint/Crit Damage</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>A &amp; D Key:</strong> Turn Left/Right</p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>S Key:</strong> Slow Down/Accuracy</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>21</strong> Different Fish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>8</strong> Unique Fish</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>5</strong> Shark Evolutions</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>15</strong> Achievements</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>3</strong> Difficulty Modes</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Should You Buy</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>How many of the following 10 points do you like?</strong><br>  </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engaging Gameplay </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Challenging Roguelike Elements </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dynamic Combat </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Progressive Leveling System </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Evolution  </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Immersive Pixel Art </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Varied Enemy Encounters </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Environment Hazards </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Boss Fight</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Replayability</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If 8-10 points:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You will love this game.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If 5-7 points:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I still feel confident recommending this game to you.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If 3-4 points:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >I’m not sure you’ll like my game. Maybe wait for a game discount.  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>If 0-2 points:</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sorry, this game is not for you.</p>",
